reviewText: Nickelodeon doesn't seem to be broadcasting Penguins of Madagascar episodes any longer and since they're not available on Verizon Fios On-Demand, I purchased all 8 available Penguins DVDs.  This one is fantastic!  It's particularly appealing for fans of the King Julien character.  Total running time is 88 minutes and the included episodes are: Happy King Julien Day!, Assaults and Batteries, Kingdom Come, Operation: Plush & Cover, Crown Fools, Jungle Law, The Helmet, and All King,No Kingdom.
summary: Penguins of Madagascar Happy King Julien Day

reviewText: As a fan of Penguins of Madagascar we get every DVD that comes out with their cartoons.  And while this one does have some good ones, you better love the King Julien character for this set of episodes.  His character gets on my nerves after awhile so it is my least favorite compilation they have released so far.  But if you are a fan then you will want this one to add to your collection.. maybe just mix it in with some of the other dvds too. :)
summary: If you like King Julien then this is your DVD
